{"tid":2231331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名小學教師被指有計劃於教材散播港獨已被取消註冊","createTime":"2020-10-05T14:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:01:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"226364ea87be9a2f3284cda517826cb0543483f2","tid":2231331,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553177-20201005.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553177-20201005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=9a5d454d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553177-20201005.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aadc9139\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553177-20201005.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，已經於9月下旬取消一名教師的註冊，指該名教師於設計的校本教案、教學材料及工作紙，有計劃地散播港獨信息。據了解，這名教師來自九龍塘宣道小學。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，經調查後，認為該名教師嚴重專業失德，指教師需要花心思設計教案、教材和工作紙，認為在課堂散播「港獨」信息並非一時疏忽，而是有計劃行為。又表示該名教師有不少教材內容扭曲和偏頗，對學生構成嚴重損害，為保障學生利益、維護教師的專業及社會大衆對教學專業團隊的信任，教育局決定取消有關教師的註冊。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，處理有關個案時，有關教師有足夠申述機會，亦有尋求法律顧問協助，局方在充分考慮申述內容後才作決定，同時局方認為涉事學校校長、副校長監管不力，已向他們發出譴責信，其他使用有關教案和教學材料的教師亦接獲書面警告，而學校亦按校本機制懲處教師，例如將有關教師停職，延遲增薪日期、免去科主任或副校長的職位等，同時亦有部份教師離職。<br />\n<br />\n教育局自去年6月至今年8月，接獲247宗關於教師在社會事件中涉嫌專業失當的投訴，目前大致完成調查204宗個案，其中73宗不成立，21名教師接獲譴責，12名教師接獲書面警告，如果有關教師再有失德行為，局方會考慮取消他們的教師註冊。另外，局方亦分別向19名教師發出書面勸喻，以及向18名教師作出口頭提示。"},{"pid":"3365764bbdce764c95f578f4eb807ee640dc217c","tid":2231331,"uid":42767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"教署屎忽鬼政治審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c75b04aa583901c113082e6e615373f2f70c35c","tid":2231331,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108439d362e44aad31725895fa1df0092d85a6c3","tid":2231331,"uid":35508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40449bebe51bd6ecb980d39c9def9504a6fa3a0","tid":2231331,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"而<strong><span class=\"red\">學校亦按校本機制懲處教師</span></strong>，例如將有關教師停職，延遲增薪日期、免去科主任或副校長的職位等，同時亦有部份教師離職。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdccecf4faf849da9b75f418dbb8d5d8f22c83d9","tid":2231331,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5b4b65b1b48c744b5aee1417e3bdbc36de9fb2","tid":2231331,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45435769e0b823f1c8007cde6435a94407ade305","tid":2231331,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"啲工作紙內容係點？